os.zip 

These are 4 scenarios created by using my random scenario generator 
which only places objects on a map.  They all share the pix file so 
you all can get an idea of what output to expect so far.  No objects 
were supposed to have names.  Some of these scenarios do not have 
exits, and I promise you that some editing is needed for playing any 
of these scenarios because objects being outside of borders.

Note: The map file was deliberately chosen to be the way it was to 
lower the amount of editing necessary before "testing" any of these 
scenarios.
